ages/terahertz-biophotonics-understanding-the-path-towards-practical-applications-for-biological-imaging3.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jun 2026 13:21:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/terahertz-biophotonics-understanding-the-path-towards-practical-applications-for-biological-imaging</guid></item><item><title>月球轨道器概念可能会在两年内揭示月球上的五个关键要素</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/lunar-orbiter-concept-could-reveal-five-key-elements-across-moon-in-two-years</link><description>东京都立大学的研究人员通过模拟表明，新开发的紧凑型 X 射线望远镜可用于绘制整个月球表面的化学成分图，这是了解月球地质演化的重要突破。探测器的详细建模和现实的卫星任务表明，两年足以绘制五个关键要素的地图，而 5×5 探测器阵列可以提高分辨率并更快地获得结果。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/lunar-orbiter-concept-could-reveal-five-key-elements-across-moon-in-two-years2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jun 2026 13:06:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/lunar-orbiter-concept-could-reveal-five-key-elements-across-moon-in-two-years</guid></item><item><title>过热的岩浆可以解释为什么相似的火山以截然不同的方式喷发</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/superheated-magma-may-explain-why-similar-volcanoes-erupt-in-very-different-ways</link><description>科学家们揭示了岩浆中的热过程，这可能有助于解释为什么相似的火山系统会产生截然不同的喷发行为。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/superheated-magma-may-explain-why-similar-volcanoes-erupt-in-very-different-ways2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jun 2026 12:51:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/superheated-magma-may-explain-why-similar-volcanoes-erupt-in-very-different-ways</guid></item><item><title>新发现的手术期间脑血流视图可以预防虚弱，挽救生命</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/newly-discovered-view-of-brain-blood-flow-during-surgery-could-prevent-debilitation-save-lives</link><description>在神经外科手术期间追踪大脑的血流是手术中最关键和最具挑战性的部分之一。短暂的中断可能意味着永久性损伤和完全恢复之间的差异，但很难追踪整个手术区域的血流。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/newly-discovered-view-of-brain-blood-flow-during-surgery-could-prevent-debilitation-save-lives.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jun 2026 12:36:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/newly-discovered-view-of-brain-blood-flow-during-surgery-could-prevent-debilitation-save-lives</guid></item><item><title>【Qstr研讨会系列】伊藤浩介 20260508</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/qstr-seminar-series-kosuke-ito-20260508</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jun 2026 12:21:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/qstr-seminar-series-kosuke-ito-20260508</guid></item><item><title>无添加剂、无盐水排放的光热海水淡化，同时从海水中完成矿物开采</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/additive-free-and-brine-discharge-free-solar-thermal-desalination-with-simultaneous-complete-mineral-mining-from-ocean-water</link><description>唐 L.、辛格 SC、魏 R. &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/additive-free-and-brine-discharge-free-solar-thermal-desalination-with-simultaneous-complete-mineral-mining-from-ocean-water2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jun 2026 12:06:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/additive-free-and-brine-discharge-free-solar-thermal-desalination-with-simultaneous-complete-mineral-mining-from-ocean-water</guid></item><item><title>科学家认为他们已经发现人类如何恢复失去的视力</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/scientists-think-theyve-discovered-how-humans-could-recover-lost-vision</link><description>哺乳动物并不以眼睛再生能力而闻名，但一项研究表明，大自然有一些秘诀。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/scientists-think-theyve-discovered-how-humans-could-recover-lost-vision2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jun 2026 11:51:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/scientists-think-theyve-discovered-how-humans-could-recover-lost-vision</guid></item></channel><